{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Roland, are you still studying this female?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: 'Pretty interesting, huh? Not really dead, but not alive either. In that state, how does she see herself...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: '...and see this world? I am quite interested in this.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: 'Save the research for later. Miss Luna wants us to gather.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "It's that one from before, right? I was just about to report to her about the Venus Splash Park.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lamia', 3: 'Then Gestalt... I mean, what about Huaxu? You managed to get it with a lot of trouble, but are you going to set it aside for now?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: "It is Miss Luna's will.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Roland', 3: "You would think that I'd be worried that things will get worse the longer it gets dragged out... but it is Miss Luna's decision, so be it.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: "It's as you just heard. Gabriel and I will go first. The rest of the preparations are in your hands.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'Preparations...?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'I\'m talking about the part that\'s related to Gestalt. What we have is just the "key" after all. The location of the main body is our problem.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lamia', 3: 'Do you have to? If you ask Lady Luna, will she answer for sure?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Roland', 3: 'If we just wait around for the answer to be announced, we won\'t even know how we\'ve died. You don\'t want to become like "that guy" right?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Gabriel', 3: "I'm counting on you, Lamia.", 4: '1'}
{3: "Gabriel ceremoniously takes off his hat and follows Roland's footsteps to the exit, then their footsteps fade."}
